        <Nerangs id="ritualNerangs">
            <ab>VrS87.5 (mss. 2005, 2007, 2010, 2030, 2040, 2101, 2109, 4000, 4010, 4025, 4040, 4050, 4055, 4060, 4161, 4162, 5020):</ab>
            <ab class="ab_indent">rāspīg pad gāh ī srōšāwarzān <em>yaθā ahū vairiiō yō zaōtā</em> tā gyaḡ zōt <em>aθā ratuš</em> kardan rāspīg <em>səraōšō iδā astū</em></ab>
            <ab class="ab_indent">"The <em>rāspīg</em> (should recite) at the place of the <em>srōšāwarz: yaθā ahū vairiiō yō zaōtā</em> until the end and the <em>zōt</em> should 
                answer: <em>aθā ratuš</em>. The <em>rāspīg</em> should recite: <em>səraōšō iδā astū</em>."</ab>
        </Nerangs>
